# Rate Limiting, Business Logic & Dashboard Fixes — Walkthrough

## What was done

Audited all 101 routes for rate limiting, handler patterns, business logic, and dashboard connections. Implemented fixes across 10 files + 1 new utility.

## Changes

### New: In-Memory Rate Limiter
| File | Purpose |
|---|---|
| [rateLimit.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/lib/rateLimit.ts) | IP-based rate limiter with auto-cleanup. [checkRateLimit(req, action, max)](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/lib/rateLimit.ts#89-121) returns 429 Response when exceeded |

### Rate limiting applied to auth routes
| Route | Limit | Why |
|---|---|---|
| [register](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/auth/register/route.ts) | 5/min/IP | Prevents registration flooding |
| [send-otp](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/auth/send-otp/route.ts) | 3/min/IP | + existing 60s DB cooldown — prevents email bombing |
| [verify-otp](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/auth/verify-otp/route.ts) | 5/min/IP | Prevents brute-forcing 6-digit codes (1M combos) |

### Security: Self-Mark Batch Verification
| File | Fix |
|---|---|
| [self-mark](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/student/attendance/self-mark/route.ts) | **Bug**: Any student could mark attendance for any batch's session. **Fix**: Verify student.batch matches attendance.batch before allowing self-mark |

### Attendance Validation Hardening
| File | Fix |
|---|---|
| [admin/attendance](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/admin/attendance/route.ts) | PUT: status whitelisted to `present/absent/late/excused`. PATCH: action whitelisted to `lock/unlock` |
| [teacher/attendance](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/teacher/attendance/%5BassignmentId%5D/route.ts) | POST: safe JSON parse, per-record status validation, fixed `marked_by` TS type |

### Admin Dashboard
| File | Fix |
|---|---|
| [admin/stats](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/admin/stats/route.ts) | Added `pendingStudents` and `rejectedStudents` counts |

## Verification

- **Build**: `npm run build` passed clean (exit code 0)
